What do we do with this information? The information is primarily used to improve our site for the purpose of better serving our valued customers.
Occasionally we will use the information to send our customers an e-mail announcement.
This e-mail may contain new product introductions and/or exclusive offers specifically tailored for the vehicles they own.
For example: We don't want to send you a special deal on a Jeep top, if you drive a Dodge Ram.
